639
00:43:34,343 --> 00:43:35,943
Ruoxi...

640
00:43:38,543 --> 00:43:40,063
Ruoxi.

641
00:43:42,783 --> 00:43:44,903
Fourth Prince.

642
00:43:48,283 --> 00:43:49,483
Ruoxi.

643
00:43:49,483 --> 00:43:51,983
Physician! Quick take a look!

644
00:44:00,743 --> 00:44:02,343
Your Majesty, please don't be anxious,

645
00:44:02,343 --> 00:44:04,183
