646
00:44:04,183 --> 00:44:06,843
I will attend to her immediately.

647
00:44:06,843 --> 00:44:07,743
Quick!

648
00:44:14,603 --> 00:44:16,983
Don't be too worried.

649
00:44:16,983 --> 00:44:19,283
Nothing will happen to Ruoxi.

650
00:44:43,663 --> 00:44:45,363
Qiaohui.

651
00:44:45,363 --> 00:44:47,983
Second Miss.

652
00:44:47,983 --> 00:44:50,303
Second Miss, you're awake.

653
00:44:55,503 --> 00:44:57,343
It's been hard on you.

654
00:44:57,343 --> 00:45:01,343
Second Miss, I slipped up.

655
00:45:02,583 --> 00:45:05,543
If I were not so worried about you,

656
00:45:05,543 --> 00:45:08,103
I would have gone to look for Madam to ask for forgiveness.

657
00:45:08,103 --> 00:45:12,323
No. Where are the others?

658
00:45:12,323 --> 00:45:14,023
Mei Xiang and Ju Yue are preparing the medicine.

659
00:45:14,023 --> 00:45:15,623
The Emperor is attending court.

660
00:45:15,623 --> 00:45:17,223
Other than attending to court matters,

661
00:45:17,223 --> 00:45:19,263
