670
00:45:42,023 --> 00:45:44,163
What's the point of having you by my side then?

671
00:45:44,163 --> 00:45:45,863
Second Miss.

672
00:45:45,863 --> 00:45:48,103
I helped 8th Fujin to pass along a message

673
00:45:48,103 --> 00:45:50,143
