674
00:45:50,143 --> 00:45:51,783
I...

675
00:45:53,443 --> 00:45:56,043
It's not your fault.

676
00:45:57,123 --> 00:45:58,523
A lot of things

677
00:45:58,523 --> 00:46:00,903
cannot be avoided, no matter what.

678
00:46:00,903 --> 00:46:03,683
There is no effect without a cause.

679
00:46:03,683 --> 00:46:08,343
You don't know the story in between, that's why you're blaming yourself.

680
00:46:08,343 --> 00:46:11,063
But it actually had nothing to do with you at all.

681
00:46:12,063 --> 00:46:14,123
13th Prince asked me privately,

682
00:46:14,123 --> 00:46:16,903
