683
00:46:16,903 --> 00:46:19,583
I said that I didn't know.

684
00:46:19,583 --> 00:46:21,423
He only told me,

685
00:46:21,423 --> 00:46:24,503
not to have anything to do with her anymore in the future.

686
00:46:24,503 --> 00:46:27,103
His Majesty was only concerned about your health

687
00:46:27,103 --> 00:46:29,743
