688
00:46:29,743 --> 00:46:32,463
I also did not dare ask.

689
00:46:32,463 --> 00:46:35,343
Does he know that I met with 8th Fujin?

690
00:46:37,343 --> 00:46:39,263
I don't know.

691
00:46:42,423 --> 00:46:43,803
Lady is awake!

692
00:46:43,803 --> 00:46:45,503
The physician said that she would wake up today.

